LylaDialogue: ^CIELLE: What?? The pink is right in my face
^LYLA: Apologies ! I am in a very excited mood so I’m a bit brighter than usual. Is this your first Aster festival visit? I don’t think I’ve seen you around?
^CIELLE: Yes it is ! We only just got here-
^LYLA: Oh? OH yes this is the landmark of this market and this festival !!
^CIELLE: It’s beautiful ! and not freaky at all aha… who are the people around it?
^LYLA: Those people are our descendants ! The Pluvia, the Navemar and the Humans created the peace treaty here in this very place!
TheRest: ^CIELLE:What happened before this market was set up?
^LYLA: Hehe... well it's no fun if I tell you straight away, there’s a bunch about the history of the market around here.
^COSMO: I mean, as much as it’d be convenient if you told us now I do want to get my hands on some new data for my logs.
